title: "Egg Production"

```{r}
# Or read in the data manually
library(tidyverse)
library(skimr)

eggproduction  <- readr::read_csv('https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rfordatascience/tidytuesday/master/data/2023/2023-04-11/egg-production.csv')
cagefreepercentages <- readr::read_csv('https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rfordatascience/tidytuesday/master/data/2023/2023-04-11/cage-free-percentages.csv')

```

## Skim the Data

`eggproduction` has no missing values. 

```{r}
skimr::skim(eggproduction)

```

```{r}
skimr::skim(cagefreepercentages)

```

```{r}
eggproduction |> janitor::tabyl(prod_process, prod_type)
```
